WEBVTT

00:03.280 --> 00:05.528
Mr. Skokie, this is Chuck Palmer

00:05.554 --> 00:07.678
with the city of Modesto
Robbery/Homicide Division.

00:07.703 --> 00:09.529
You're going to see a
table with a body on it.

00:09.554 --> 00:12.225
I need you to tell me if
the body you see is your son.

00:12.250 --> 00:13.716
That's Matt.

00:13.752 --> 00:15.351
Is Gwen dead? Gwen's at the hospital.

00:15.387 --> 00:18.421
There are indications she
was sexually assaulted.

00:18.457 --> 00:19.789
Have you called his mother yet?

00:19.825 --> 00:21.105
Well, what are the police doing?

00:21.126 --> 00:22.859
We have four suspects in custody...

00:22.894 --> 00:26.296
Two who facilitated and one
who we believe is the shooter.

00:26.331 --> 00:28.131
I'm serving you with a notice of petition

00:28.166 --> 00:30.767
- to take possession of the remains of Matthew Skokie.
- What?

00:30.802 --> 00:32.101
I need you to get here, Mark.

00:32.137 --> 00:33.707
Okay, mom. I'll fly back as soon as I can.

00:33.732 --> 00:35.316
And you want to talk about
whether she was raped,

00:35.341 --> 00:36.902
- whether she wasn't raped.
- Yes, I do.

00:36.927 --> 00:38.675
- Why? What difference does it make?
- Because that is not

00:38.710 --> 00:40.043
- the child that I raised...
- Don't do it!

00:40.078 --> 00:41.311
Don't do it to her! Don't!

00:41.346 --> 00:42.979
Your son doesn't even
want to visit with you.

00:43.014 --> 00:44.314
How are you going to help him if
he doesn't want to talk to you?

00:44.349 --> 00:45.753
Yo, Tina!

00:45.778 --> 00:47.138
Come on. Get up. don't be a bitch.

00:47.146 --> 00:48.746
When are they gonna sign me out of here?

00:48.747 --> 00:49.949
Five weeks, six at most.

00:49.957 --> 00:51.890
You're gonna get counseling,
and you are going to engage

00:51.926 --> 00:53.806
your mother and your
brother when they get here.

00:53.827 --> 00:55.916
No, I'm gonna get you a lawyer
that's working for a cause,

00:55.941 --> 00:57.507
not a dollar.

00:57.542 --> 01:00.176
You take their drugs, you
sleep with their women,

01:00.212 --> 01:02.412
and then they put you in their cage.

01:02.447 --> 01:04.114
Don't come in here with your
fake-ass religion nonsense.

01:04.149 --> 01:05.348
What I believe is real.

01:12.424 --> 01:15.625
These are hard times.

01:15.660 --> 01:18.995
Hard times.

01:19.064 --> 01:23.466
Daily, we see the suffering of our people.

01:23.502 --> 01:28.438
We can testify to the inequities
our community lives with.

01:28.473 --> 01:32.142
Daily, our young brothers
are treated like criminals.

01:32.177 --> 01:35.211
Treated like animals.

01:35.247 --> 01:38.646
Even unarmed and innocent.

01:39.202 --> 01:40.635
Far too often,

01:40.671 --> 01:44.205
they are the ones left
shot dead in the street.

01:44.241 --> 01:47.709
We are not people to the oppressors.

01:47.744 --> 01:49.644
But we are not victims, either,

01:49.680 --> 01:53.014
my honorable brothers
and my beloved sisters.

01:53.050 --> 01:55.317
We are the original ones.

01:55.352 --> 01:59.020
He who is called the Messiah...

01:59.056 --> 02:02.624
The Mahdi, the Christ...

02:02.659 --> 02:05.860
He comes from us.

02:05.896 --> 02:07.796
He looks as we look.

02:10.100 --> 02:13.101
And I charge you to go
out into the greater world

02:13.136 --> 02:16.771
and... and achieve great
things for our people.

02:16.807 --> 02:19.808
"'Not by might nor by power,

02:19.843 --> 02:23.859
but by my spirit, ' saith the lord"!

02:23.884 --> 02:25.750
All praises to Allah!

02:25.786 --> 02:28.386
All praises to Allah!

02:28.422 --> 02:29.988
All praises to Allah!

02:30.023 --> 02:32.557
All praises to Allah!

