- It isn't my choice. It was the judge's decision.

23:57.550 --> 23:58.605
Who brought it to the judge?

23:58.641 --> 24:00.374
The defense made a bail review application,

24:00.409 --> 24:02.376
and the judge decided to revisit the issue.

24:02.411 --> 24:04.073
Can't... can't you do something to stop it?

24:04.098 --> 24:05.498
They have a right to a hearing.

24:05.533 --> 24:07.299
But you'd better believe I'll fight back.

24:07.335 --> 24:09.971
Look... the fact that the gun doesn't match

24:09.996 --> 24:12.104
doesn't exculpate him,
doesn't mean he's innocent.

24:12.140 --> 24:13.439
It raises questions...

24:13.474 --> 24:16.142
But the fact that he had a gun,
I mean, that... that shows...

24:16.177 --> 24:17.476
He could have had two guns,

24:17.512 --> 24:18.811
used one for the murder and
then another one at home.

24:18.846 --> 24:20.579
It's also possible, of course.

24:20.615 --> 24:22.415
He still could have raped Gwen.
He could have used a condom.

24:22.450 --> 24:24.429
All of that... those are
arguments I'll make to the judge.

24:24.454 --> 24:26.020
Did you find a condom?

24:26.738 --> 24:29.870
No, but that doesn't mean one wasn't used.

24:29.925 --> 24:33.265
We'll continue to investigate
and build our case against him.

24:33.300 --> 24:35.066
We still have Hector Tontz,

24:35.102 --> 24:37.669
who places Mr. Nix near
the scene of the crime

24:37.704 --> 24:39.805
and in possession of Matt's wallet.

24:39.840 --> 24:42.107
Those are very strong pieces of evidence.

24:42.142 --> 24:43.742
But in the meantime,
he could still get out.

24:43.777 --> 24:45.043
Well, there's absolutely

24:45.078 --> 24:46.344
