25:14.409 --> 25:17.776
- The police interviewed the men that Gwen was sleeping with.
- What?

25:17.801 --> 25:20.436
- They told me that neither of them is a suspect.
- What did you say?

25:20.461 --> 25:22.902
Uh, Gwen was unfaithful to your brother.

25:22.927 --> 25:24.631
Well, your son was the one, actually,
who broke his vow to protect...

25:24.666 --> 25:26.749
We've all found out things
