25:34.543 --> 25:36.265
Just please know we will.

25:38.359 --> 25:39.890
The bail hearing is Friday.

25:40.827 --> 25:42.765
I assure you... we'll be ready.

25:46.740 --> 25:48.822
Well, I don't trust him anymore.

25:48.857 --> 25:50.924
What the hell is he talking about...

25:50.959 --> 25:52.138
"Matt's lifestyle"?

25:52.163 --> 25:54.631
