what he's talking about.

25:54.656 --> 25:56.556
No, Tom, I don't. Do you?

25:56.581 --> 25:57.941
They found drugs in the house.

25:57.966 --> 25:59.899
- They say they did.
- They found them.

25:59.935 --> 26:02.168
- They say.
- Gwen said.

26:02.204 --> 26:05.939
- Gwen told me that Matt was selling drugs, okay?
- Yeah.

26:05.974 --> 26:07.874
