27:09.878 --> 27:10.877
- Let's have it.
- Let's have it.

27:10.913 --> 27:12.512
Let's have that conversation, Barb,

27:12.548 --> 27:14.314
because the things Gwen's told me...

27:14.349 --> 27:16.160
- Oh, the things she's said.
- What? What did she...

27:16.185 --> 27:19.853
If you really want to talk
about truth and lies, Barb,

27:19.888 --> 27:22.102
then we should talk!

27:22.127 --> 27:23.868
But you need to go first.

27:23.893 --> 27:25.994
Everybody done?

27:26.029 --> 27:28.096
You done blaming each other?

27:28.131 --> 27:29.597
Yeah, I gambled.

27:29.633 --> 27:34.502
That's got nothing to do
with my son getting killed.

27:34.537 --> 27:36.804
Matt and Gwen deserve better
than what happened to them,

27:36.840 --> 27:41.476
and they deserve better than
what we're doing right here.

27:41.865 --> 27:43.331
Gwen's gonna survive,

27:43.356 --> 27:45.772
and she's gonna need you every day.

27:47.517 --> 27:50.151
Maybe it's for the best.

27:51.521 --> 27:53.988
At least that way she
won't be able to... around.

27:54.024 --> 27:56.491
Oh, my god.

27:56.788 --> 27:59.083
You can drag down your
daughter if you want.

27:59.108 --> 28:01.029
