30:23.763 --> 30:26.664
The sky was truly blue.
The temperature was right.

30:26.700 --> 30:27.999
Yeah.

30:29.469 --> 30:31.536
I'm grateful for my freedom.

30:33.506 --> 30:37.041
And... I want freedom for all of us.

30:41.806 --> 30:44.006
I know you're not on good
terms with your husband,

30:44.041 --> 30:45.941
but you have to sit next to him, okay?

30:45.977 --> 30:48.544
- I can do that. My son is here, too.
- Good.

30:48.579 --> 30:50.679
